                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Domitio <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Sal<lb break="no" n="2"/>lentino aedili IIviro <lb n="3"/>curatori alimentorum <lb n="4"/>et partis <expan><abbr>kalendari</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> publici <lb n="5"/>patrono coloniae optimo et <lb n="6"/>praestantissimo et civi<lb break="no" n="7"/>um suorum amantissimo cu<lb break="no" n="8"/>ius cura et auxilio et res <lb n="9"/>publica aucta <lb n="10"/>et omnibus <lb n="11"/>commodis municip<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>um</abbr></expan> pro<lb break="no" n="12"/>spectum est <lb n="13"/>decurionum decreto publice
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
